'''酸奶油'''是一种奶制品，由[[鮮奶油|奶油]]和[[乳酸菌|乳酸菌]]发酵而成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://homecooking.about.com/od/milkproducts/a/sourcreamwhatis.htm |title=What is sour cream. Sour cream for cooking recipes |publisher=Homecooking.about.com |date=2010-06-14 |accessdate=2011-09-14 |archive-date=2016-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101130058/http://homecooking.about.com/od/milkproducts/a/sourcreamwhatis.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。因发酵的乳酸菌和酸味得名（Sour cream）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://homecooking.about.com/od/milkproducts/a/sourcreamwhatis.htm|title=What is sour cream?|publisher=[[About.com|About.com]]|language=en|accessdate=2011-02-15|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101130058/http://homecooking.about.com/od/milkproducts/a/sourcreamwhatis.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。酸奶油口感丝滑，味道接近[[酸奶|酸奶]]和[[克非尔|克非尔]]的混合。脂肪含量仅10%，是最清淡的奶油制品。每100克酸奶油仅含190卡路里。像大多数其他酸牛奶产品一样，酸奶油最初来自[[东欧|东欧]]和[[斯堪的那维亚|斯堪的那维亚]]。酸奶油需要冷藏，开封后能保存一周。

